Of course, the problem with parallel universes is that .. as soon as you observe them, they change direction.
&nbsp;
Then again, there is a better way of communicating with parallel realities. Whatever can happen, will happen .. but some things are more likely to happen than others .. and the things that are more likely to happen, occupy more volume in the multiverse.
&nbsp;
Thus - if you measure infinity, by volume and percentages .. you can, in fact, measure infinity!

1527317186_1Kma1Pz9kBSHmDtK1iYtHTox14Edm.body:
Simply put - you could create a computer that can see into the future.
&nbsp;
..problem is, as soon as you see the future - you're tempted to change it .. and when you're tempted to change it...

1527351127_19Qid9uyfWCTmx2cUpDboEKCscRd4.body:
Now that I think about it, ZeroNet actually provides the perfect environment for us to study the psychology of Pedophilia.
&nbsp;
Instead of hunting down pedophiles, why don't we study them? Maybe this way, we could find a cure, and/or a cause.
&nbsp;
Game theory could help a lot, in this case.. now that I've mentioned it before.

If you want to reduce child pornography, you need to look for the reason people are drawn to it in the first place.
&nbsp;
As I said, there is more maths behind people's decisions, than you like to think.

1527370955_1Kma1Pz9kBSHmDtK1iYtHTox14Edm.body:
However, with Artificial Intelligence, Machine Learning and Robotics .. the job is done for you.
&nbsp;
Therefore - the only way to escape the grid, is to be as high-tech as possible. Otherwise, you will fail. That is, IF your reason for escaping the grid, is to escape work.
